          ],
          "text": "where the dot represents a via. Here, both traces are dangling, but they have two graph edges each: each other, and the via. In fact, any number of traces could come together at the via, and they would all be dangling but not detected as such.",
          "uuid": "c46069e8"
        }
      ]
    },
